=So Clumsy, How Will You Be My Lady One Day=

11
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,400
Shiyue.

12
00:01:47,320 --> 00:01:48,240
Shiyue!

13
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:51,520
Shiyue...

14
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,240
Come.

15
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:54,760
Come here.

16
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,840
Come to me.

17
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:59,680
Your mom and I are waiting for you.

18
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:01,560
My precious daughter,

19
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:02,920
come over quickly.

20
00:02:03,450 --> 00:02:05,460
Our family can finally be reunited.

21
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,360
You're the only one left.

22
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:08,840
What's wrong?

23
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:10,680
Don't you miss me?

24
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,280
I've been missing you.

25
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:15,880
Where is my elder sister?

26
00:02:17,060 --> 00:02:18,320
Forget about her.

27
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,760
Come here now.

28
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:23,320
Avenge us.

29
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:49,200
Shiyue.

30
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,280
Shiyue!

31
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,600
It's alright. I'm here.

32
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:58,280
Dad, run!

33
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,800
It's over now. I'm here.

34
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:02,110
♪Spring comes late after the snow♪

35
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,040
Shiyue.

36
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:06,800
♪Through all the joy and sorrow♪

37
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:11,270
♪Stories untold on the busy street♪

38
00:03:11,270 --> 00:03:14,490
♪Lost you as I turned♪

39
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:18,740
♪Through a haze of dust♪

40
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:22,400
♪Reunion masked by moonlight♪

41
00:03:23,230 --> 00:03:27,000
♪Cold or tender♪

42
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:30,320
♪Crowds push us apart♪

43
00:03:30,330 --> 00:03:31,860
Young Marshal, the checkup's all clear.

44
00:03:32,100 --> 00:03:33,460
The bullet passed through
the right chest

45
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:34,240
and missed vital organs.

46
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:36,800
But it may affect heavy labor
in the future.

47
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,640
When will she wake up?

48
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,440
Though her life is not in danger,

49
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:43,160
she lost too much blood
and may remain unconscious for days.

50
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:45,320
Clean the wound daily during this period

51
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,280
to prevent infection.

52
00:03:47,810 --> 00:03:48,680
Jinxiu,

53
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:49,840
escort Dr. Bai out.

54
00:03:50,390 --> 00:03:51,240
This way, please.

55
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:56,690
♪After splendor comes desolation♪

56
