♪I'll kiss your face♪

58
00:04:18,960 --> 00:04:20,360
My father was framed.

59
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,880
I have to clear his name.

60
00:04:22,770 --> 00:04:24,440
My whole family is gone.

61
00:04:25,370 --> 00:04:26,840
Losing me won't change a thing.

